в”‚   в”‚            Atomicity в†’ All or nothing(all transactions should pass or fail)
в”‚   в”‚            Consistency в†’ Valid state always
в”‚   в”‚            Isolation в†’ No interference(like ticket booking)
в”‚   в”‚            Durability в†’ Data is permanent
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ NoSQL в†’ Flexible schema, optimized for scalability.
в”‚   в”‚            BASE
в”‚   в”‚            Basically Available в†’ System always responds
в”‚   в”‚            Soft State в†’ Data may change over time
в”‚   в”‚            Eventual Consistency в†’ Data becomes consistent later
